videos.description: De'Andre Hunter steals the pass and heads the other way before losing the ball in transition, but he recovers nicely with a reverse and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Hunter loses handle, recovers for fast-break and-1

videos.description: Christen Cunningham finds Ryan McMahon for a 3-pointer, then McMahon drills another triple on the next possession to extend Louisville's first-half lead.
videos.headline: McMahon electrifies crowd with back-to-back 3s

videos.description: Jordan Nwora pulls up from well beyond the arc and banks in a deep 3-pointer to extend the Cardinals' lead over the Cavaliers.
videos.headline: Nwora hits from way downtown to beat first-half buzzer

videos.description: Kihei Clark connects with Jay Huff for a huge reverse alley-oop jam, then Clark finds Huff again at the end of the half for another nasty alley-oop.
videos.headline: Huff throws down two ridiculous alley-oops

videos.description: De'Andre Hunter crosses up Dwayne Sutton and drives baseline for a strong slam.
videos.headline: Hunter shakes defense for big finish

videos.description: Ty Jerome drives the lane and finds Mamadi Diakite, who rises up for the big finish to extend Virginia's lead late in the second half.
videos.headline: Diakite pads lead with rim-rocking slam
